quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alif-lam-meem"
  29,2,"Ahasiba annasu anyutrakoo an yaqooloo amanna wahum layuftanoon"
  29,3,"Walaqad fatanna allatheena minqablihim falayaAAlamanna Allahu allatheena sadaqoowalayaAAlamanna alkathibeen"
  29,4,"Am hasiba allatheenayaAAmaloona assayyi-ati an yasbiqoona saama yahkumoon"
  29,5,"Man kana yarjoo liqaa Allahifa-inna ajala Allahi laatin wahuwa assameeAAualAAaleem"
  29,6,"Waman jahada fa-innama yujahidulinafsihi inna Allaha laghaniyyun AAani alAAalameen"